    "notes": [
      "Minutes 0-11: healthy baseline",
      "Minutes 12-24: Black Friday traffic ramp begins",
      "Minutes 25-39: sustained surge; CPU and DB connections climb",
      "Minutes 40-51: connection pool pressure; latency and errors rise",
      "Minutes 52-59: payment service degrading (SLO breach, near pool exhaustion)"
    ]
